<h1>Blazor Validation Sample</h1>

<p>
    This sample demonstrates the <strong>Microsoft.Extensions.Validation</strong> framework
    with localization support in a Blazor Web application.
</p>

<h2>Features demonstrated</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Customer Form</strong> &mdash; Required, StringLength, EmailAddress, Range, Phone, and Display attribute validation</li>
    <li><strong>Order Form</strong> &mdash; IValidatableObject, custom FutureDateAttribute, and localized error messages</li>
</ul>

